<h2>YouTube Shorts for Local Businesses</h2>
<p>YouTube Shorts get over 70 billion views per day. They are vertical videos under 60 seconds that appear in a dedicated feed, in search results, and on the YouTube homepage.</p>
<h3>Why Shorts Work for Local Businesses</h3>
<p>Shorts have a lower barrier to entry than long-form videos. The algorithm shows Shorts to people who have never heard of your channel. A plumber posting a 15-second clip has the same chance of being seen as a creator with 1 million subscribers.</p>
<p>Unlike TikTok posts that peak within 24 hours, YouTube Shorts stay discoverable permanently.</p>
