<h2>Measuring YouTube Performance and ROI</h2>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="YouTube metrics that matter for local businesses showing watch time, CTR, and leads" src="/images/blog/youtube-local-metrics.webp" /></p>
<p>Views are a vanity metric for local businesses. A video with 50 views that generates 3 phone calls is more valuable than a viral video with 50,000 views and zero leads.</p>
